Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. I: Sem rychle Vesny kvet, at sochu ovencime [Festoon with flowers gay the statue of great Vesna] [Tenor]
Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. I: Ky v pozadi to hluk? [What causes all That noise?] [Chorus]

Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. I: Recitative. Vstup v nitro sve, mym domem neni zeme [Upon This earth thy search would be a vain quest] [Bass]
Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. I: Vse lame se a borti v chaos tmavy [Now everything Is crumbling, all Is chaos] [Chorus]

Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. II: Aria. Ja neklamal se, bud vitana, dcero! [No error made, I welcome you, daughter!] [Bass]

Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. II: O neklamu se, chapu juz [I think, the truth I now infer] [Chorus]
Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. II: Recitative. Ach, ona, po niz srdce moje prahne [Ah, It Is she for whom my heart Is yearning] [Tenor, Bass]
Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. II: Aria. O, cestu ukaz mi, jak ji mam dobyt [Oh, show to me the way That I must win her] [Tenor]
Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. II: Recitative. O, kterak mohu zvednout k tobe zraku [How Is It possible to raise my eyelids] [Soprano]
Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. II: O beda, nechce slyset jeho lkani! [Oh, heavens! She'll not listen to his pleading!] [Chorus]
Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. II: Recitative. Jak z krasneho snu nahle procitly [I rudely awake from a perfect dream] [Tenor, Bass]
Svatá Ludmila (St. Ludmila), Op. 71, B. 144: Pt. II: Ja hledala jsem zari toho jitra [for This new shining dawn I am now searching] [Soprano, Mezzo-soprano, Tenor, Bass, Chorus]
